WEBVTT

00:10.319 --> 00:14.260
New message. 9:03am.

00:14.284 --> 00:17.072
I won't have you talking to me
like that. Not in my own home.

00:17.096 --> 00:20.096
You come back now, say you're sorry,
 or don't come back at all!

00:21.640 --> 00:24.640
End of message.

00:25.416 --> 00:27.952
You've made your point, OK?

00:27.976 --> 00:30.320
Let's just put it behind us.

00:30.344 --> 00:33.344
We both said things we didn't mean.

00:34.444 --> 00:37.104
And me and your dad just want you
to come home now.

00:37.128 --> 00:40.128
End of message.

00:40.264 --> 00:43.264
Tonia, where are you?

00:43.528 --> 00:46.528
You're scaring us.
We just want to know you're safe.

00:46.600 --> 00:49.600
Yeah? Give us a call.
Will you do that?

00:52.040 --> 00:55.040
End of message.

00:56.328 --> 00:59.328
We want you home.

00:59.720 --> 01:01.424
We're both worried sick.

01:01.448 --> 01:03.536
Just come home.

01:03.560 --> 01:06.560
End of message.

01:08.808 --> 01:11.808
Darling, we want you to come home.

01:19.048 --> 01:22.048
We love you so much.

01:25.512 --> 01:28.512
Tonia, please come home, baby.

